OL,3,CThe Rolling Stones level with The
OL,4,CBeatles after landing 15th UK number
OL,5,Cone album
OL,7,FThe Rolling Stones have pulled level
OL,8,Fwith The Beatles for number one
OL,9,Frecords.
OL,11,FThe band, which formed in London more
OL,12,Fthan six decades ago, landed their
OL,13,F15th chart-topping album, according to
OL,14,Fthe Official Charts Company.
OL,16,FThe 14-track record ` titled Foreign
OL,17,FTongues ` follows on from their 2023
OL,18,Frelease Hackney Diamonds, and has been
OL,19,Fwidely praised by critics as a late-
OL,20,Fcareer peak.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G1/11
