PN,37802
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F378A1784638109
OL,3,CThe Rolling Stones level with The
OL,4,CBeatles after landing 15th UK number
OL,5,Cone album
OL,7,FThe record was released on Friday and
OL,8,Fhas already shot to the top of the
OL,9,Fcharts, meaning the Grammy-winning
OL,10,Fgroup has now earned the same amount
OL,11,Fof number one albums as fellow 1960s
OL,12,Frockers The Beatles.
OL,14,FThe group is widely regarded as one of
OL,15,Fthe greatest rock and roll bands of
OL,16,Fall time, and is comprised of singer
OL,17,FSir Mick Jagger and guitarists Keith
OL,18,FRichards and Ronnie Wood.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G2/11
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
