PN,37804
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F378A1784638109
OL,3,CThe Rolling Stones level with The
OL,4,CBeatles after landing 15th UK number
OL,5,Cone album
OL,7,FThe seven-member ensemble said their
OL,8,Ftop 10 feat is "still hard to get our
OL,9,Fheads around", adding: "Seeing our
OL,10,Fname in the official albums chart
OL,11,Falongside artists like The Rolling
OL,12,FStones is a proper pinch-me moment.
OL,14,F"Then you go to a record shop signing
OL,15,Fand there are hundreds of people
OL,16,Fwaiting to meet you and get their
OL,17,Frecord or CD signed."Those are the
OL,18,Fmoments that make you stop and think,
OL,19,F'Wow... this is really actually
OL,20,Fhappening.'"
