OL,3,CThe Rolling Stones level with The
OL,4,CBeatles after landing 15th UK number
OL,5,Cone album
OL,7,FElsewhere on the official albums
OL,8,Fchart, US rock band My Chemical
OL,9,FRomance sits at number two with a
OL,10,Fremastered version of their 2010
OL,11,Frecord Danger Days: The True Lives Of
OL,12,FThe Fabulous Killjoys.
OL,14,FFollowing at number three is Olivia
OL,15,FRodrigo with her chart-topping album
OL,16,FYou Seem Pretty Sad For A Girl So In
OL,17,FLove ` which landed her the biggest
OL,18,Fopening week of her career after its
OL,19,Frelease last month.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G6/11
