OL,3,CThe Rolling Stones level with The
OL,4,CBeatles after landing 15th UK number
OL,5,Cone album
OL,7,FOasis' Wonderwall, which has been
OL,8,Fadopted by England fans throughout the
OL,9,F2026 Fifa World Cup as an unofficial
OL,10,Fanthem for the men's national team,
OL,11,Fsits at two.
OL,13,FIt comes after Thomas Tuchel's men
OL,14,Fsuffered a heartbreaking 2-1 loss
OL,15,Fagainst Argentina during the semi-
OL,16,Ffinal match on Wednesday, dashing
OL,17,FEngland's hopes of ending a 60-year
OL,18,Fwait for World Cup glory.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G9/11
