OL,7,FThree Lions by David Baddiel, Frank
OL,8,FSkinner and the Lightning Seeds `
OL,9,Fwhich has been a football anthem since
OL,10,Fits 1996 release, is at three as World
OL,11,FCup fever takes over the charts.
OL,13,FIt is followed by Talk To You by Anotr/
OL,14,F54 Ultra at four, while the official
OL,15,Fanthem of the football tournament `
OL,16,FDai Dai by Shakira and Burna Boy `
OL,17,Frounds off the top five.
